vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting the creation of a new subdistrict, Lawyers Building, within the West End Historic Sign District on a property zoned CA-1(A) Central Area District with Historic Overlay No. 2, on the southwest corner of Main Street and South Austin Street
Recommendation of Staff:  Approval
Recommendation of CPC:  Approval, subject to conditions
SPSD234-003(OA)
